translations: 计算，估算（compute 的过去式和过去分词）

sentences.sentence: All the checks are computed automatically in the system.
sentences.translation: 所有的支票都是在系统中自动计算的。

sentences.sentence: This tax, which was assessed on villages, was computed by the central government using the annual census figures.
sentences.translation: 这项对村庄征收的税是由中央政府根据年度人口普查数据计算出来的。

sentences.sentence: Notwithstanding, all nicety of calculations, the real course of Uranus would not at all agree with the one computed.
sentences.translation: 不过，即使是完全准确的计算，其结果与天王星的实际运行轨迹也并不完全一致。
